      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a champ. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been well-cared for, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. It runs like a dream and is ready for many more miles of memories. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come check it out!",
      "price": 34500.0,
