    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit exhibits crisp throttle response and linear power delivery through the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for structural integrity. The suspension retains its factory-spec McPherson struts and multi-link rear setup, providing excellent lateral grip. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals remain robust, including a healthy M Variable Differential Lock. A visceral, high-revving machine for the serious purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
