      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, showing only the minor road wear expected from a well-loved driver. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium upholstery is free of tears, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system\u2014operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is rock solid. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection just completed to ensure total peace of mind. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two keys, and a comprehensive folder of service records. If you are looking for a reliable, high-performing vehicle that balances luxury with practical value, this is an outstanding choice.",
